{
  "texts": [
    "Table 6 Ablation on rubrics.",
    "We ablate the rubrics used during RL training, and the effect of adding evolving rubrics.",
    "We find that using simple rubrics can actually hurt performance, while search-based rubrics perform best.",
    "Further adding evolving rubrics gives a one point improvement on average.",
    "For expensive training costs, we stopped this ablation after 650 steps and switched to training with evolving rubrics for longer."
  ]
}